1
00:00:03,670 --> 00:00:06,673
Is he only this talkative
when he's sleeping in?

2
00:00:06,673 --> 00:00:08,408
Now that he's awake,
he's gone silent.

3
00:00:10,076 --> 00:00:11,478
What's the next task?

4
00:00:13,947 --> 00:00:15,548
A selfie. Give me your phone.

5
00:00:22,222 --> 00:00:23,056
Here.

6
00:00:34,968 --> 00:00:35,702
I tagged you.

7
00:00:38,004 --> 00:00:38,638
If you're gonna post, fine,

8
00:00:38,638 --> 00:00:39,639
but why tag me?

9
00:00:41,641 --> 00:00:42,642
Consider it a little payback.

10
00:00:42,642 --> 00:00:45,712
I spent all night taking care of you.

11
00:00:46,179 --> 00:00:47,781
I'm the one who sacrificed.

12
00:00:48,681 --> 00:00:50,483
Let me see which one you posted.

13
00:00:52,852 --> 00:00:53,720
Hey!

14
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:55,355
This one is hideous.

15
00:00:55,655 --> 00:00:56,890
You made me look so bad.

16
00:00:59,159 --> 00:01:00,026
Let me do it.

17
00:01:01,394 --> 00:01:02,929
There's no rule on how to take it.

18
00:01:04,631 --> 00:01:05,732
Just work with me here.

19
00:01:06,399 --> 00:01:07,300
Lean in a bit.

20
00:01:10,070 --> 00:01:11,271
Smile.

21
00:01:22,348 --> 00:01:23,583
Why did you "like" that?

22
00:01:24,117 --> 00:01:25,418
You're doing this on purpose.

23
00:01:28,761 --> 00:01:31,795
[The fans go crazy over their bait]

24
00:01:34,661 --> 00:01:35,628
"The perfect match."

25
00:01:37,297 --> 00:01:38,298
We're not a match.

26
00:01:38,298 --> 00:01:39,232
Why wouldn't we be?

27
00:01:39,232 --> 00:01:40,366
In what way are we?

28
00:01:40,366 --> 00:01:41,434
The fans said so.

29
00:01:41,434 --> 00:01:43,503
Height, looks, zodiac, blood type...

30
00:01:44,571 --> 00:01:45,672
or even

31
00:01:46,272 --> 00:01:47,340
family background.

32
00:01:48,308 --> 00:01:49,375
We don't match.

33
00:01:52,899 --> 00:01:54,581
You don't actually...

34
00:01:54,581 --> 00:01:57,016
like me, do you?

35
00:01:59,252 --> 00:02:01,421
If I really did,

36
00:02:02,155 --> 00:02:03,123
would you accept it?

37
00:02:06,259 --> 00:02:07,627
You actors...

38
00:02:07,627 --> 00:02:09,128
flirting first thing in the morning.

39
00:02:09,128 --> 00:02:10,396
You're really something.

40
00:02:13,933 --> 00:02:15,068
Here. What is it?

41
00:02:16,336 --> 00:02:19,405
Task five is a livestream.

42
00:02:21,274 --> 00:02:22,909
We can just wing it.

43
00:02:22,909 --> 00:02:24,344
It's a new official account anyway.

44
00:02:24,344 --> 00:02:25,879
I heard it's just to test the traffic.

45
00:02:27,580 --> 00:02:28,248
Give me a second.

46
00:02:28,248 --> 00:02:29,115
I'm going to go get ready.
